nodes.text: Boba Fett: A Bounty Hunter's Journey

The article Boba Fett: A Bounty Hunter's Journey was written by Leland Chee as a feature in Star Wars Insider 117. The feature contains a brief history of Boba Fett's character background development through the course of the Star Wars saga up through the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series. The article was reprinted in Star Wars Insider Special Edition 2013.
